## Account Information collection [/account/{user_id}]

### Retrieve a user [GET]
+ Parameters
    + user_id: `1` (string) - Object id string of user
+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
                "id": "12345678910" 
                "first_name": "Josh",
                "last_name": "Dando",
                "email": "josh@example.com",
                "telephone": "0771234567567",
                "contact_preferences": ["email", "post", "telephone"],
                "favourite_artists": ["Eminem", "Oasis"],
                "favourite_venues": ["O2", "Manchester Arena"],
                "ticketmaster": {
                    "email": "ticket@exmaple.com",
